                hint: '"They" is plural so it takes "are" in the present continuous.',
            },
            {
                id: '3-1-3',
                theme: 'Subject-Verb Agreement',
                q: '"He ___ like spicy food." — Choose the correct negative verb.',
                options: ["don't", "doesn't", 'do not', 'are not'],
