                hint: '"Walked" is the past simple form. The -ed ending signals past tense.',
            },
            {
                id: '3-2-5',
                theme: 'Verb Tenses',
                q: 'What is the past tense of "write"?',
                options: ['writed', 'writes', 'written', 'wrote'],
